data.description: If you are looking for a large piece of land in a quiet area with nothing but space look no further! Large living area, large bedrooms and a large office space directly off of the living area. Included is a 20x20 workshop with and an additional 10x16 storage shed. RV hook-up 30 amp electric with water and sewer access and wide driveway parking. The home is handicap accessible with features such as wide hallways and doorways.
